  • Type Parameters:
    K - Main parameter used for lookup.
    E - Specfic class used in db.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IAccountDao, IFederationDao, IFederationMemberDao, IPartDao, IScoreboardDao, IShipDao
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractJpaDao, JpaAccountDao, JpaFederationDao, JpaFederationMemberDao, JpaPartDao, JpaScoreboardDao, JpaShipDao
